name: Midnight
description: Meet Midnight, the CEO's best friend. This isn't your average German Shepherd, instead of herding sheep, Midnight is in charge of leading the Memecoin run on Polygon. He got a bite when it comes to crypto. When he's not stealing hearts (and maybe a sock or two for a strategic treat exchange), Midnight's busy attending team meetings. His investment portfolio? Diversified, of course! But his biggest love? $MATIC (gotta support the fam!).
